Text: Where is episode #8? I could usually find a new episode here every friday. Hope it didn't get canceled

After looking for Episode 8 myself I did a little research and as far as I can tell its not out until August "Scars, Part 1 August 2, 2012 108 	
Dyson, one of Clu's top men and old friend turned traitor of Tron, arrives in Argon City. Tron will not let anything stand in his way to achieve his revenge on Dyson, not even Beck.
